<seg id=1> The most Hong Kong person does not hope to call self the Chinese </seg>
</hl> 
<p> 
<seg id=2> (The Hong Kong Faxin news) one public opinion poll which announces according to yesterday demonstrates, although Hong Kong has returned China to last year, but the most Hong Kong person does not hope oneself to be called the Chinese. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=3> The poll result demonstrates, in 6500000 Hong Kong inhabitant, 40% person is called as oneself " the Hong Kong person ", 22.3% people said oneself is " the Hong Kong Chinese ", 20.6% personal own are " lives in Hong Kong's Chinese ". </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=4> Is engaged in this poll the organization is the Hong Kong University social sciences research center. </seg>
<seg id=5> In the middle 517 participants, only has 20.6% personal own is the Chinese, 1.6% people have not made clear the answer or have not expressed the view. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=6> Returns in the similar investigation after Hong Kong which half year carries on, 35.9% personal own are " the Hong Kong person ", 18% personal own are the Chinese. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=7> Hong Kong returns has had 15 months, the Hong Kong government continuously is attempting to remind the inhabitant, they are the Chinese. </seg>
<seg id=8> The Hong Kong official accuses, 150 year English colonial rule causes the very many Hong Kong inhabitant to appear awkwardly in the identity question. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=9> Hong Kong special zone administration senior official Dong Jianhua day before yesterday delivered a speech in the National Day says, " took the Chinese, I felt extremely honorable, and extremely was proud for our country development ". </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=10> In order to trains the Chinese citizen in the Hong Kong inhabitant realizes, the Hong Kong citizen educated promotes to be able to compile and to publish the abundant and elegant book " I is Chinese ". </seg>
</p> 
